propel.core.collections.stacks
Class SharedStack<T>

java.lang.Object
  propel.core.collections.stacks.SharedStack<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<T>, ReifiedIterable<T>, ISharedStack<T>, IShared
public class SharedStack<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISharedStack<T>

A shared stack for use by multiple threads. This collection allows null items to be inserted. Instantiate using e.g.: new SharedStack<String>(){}; -OR- new SharedStack<String>(String.class);
